76 Courts in some states have made it very difficult for consumers to bring actions under these 
laws.  See,  e.g.,  Zeeman  v.  Black,  273  S.E.2d  910,  915  (Ga.  Ct.  App.  1980)  (imposing  a  ‘‘public 
